trug dynamically links the following LGPL-2.1+ libraries, built from
pinned source by Scripts/build-deps.sh (versions in Scripts/deps.lock):

  libimobiledevice        https://github.com/libimobiledevice/libimobiledevice
  libusbmuxd              https://github.com/libimobiledevice/libusbmuxd
  libimobiledevice-glue   https://github.com/libimobiledevice/libimobiledevice-glue
  libplist                https://github.com/libimobiledevice/libplist

Per LGPL-2.1 §6: these libraries are dynamically linked and replaceable;
build scripts to rebuild and relink them are published in this repository.
OpenSSL 3 (Apache-2.0) is used as the TLS backend.
